 Rare offers a variety of spaces perfect for relaxed revelry.</p></div>\nsource/functions.html:2317:  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1696824135934_18523 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/functions.html:2360:          #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1696824135934_18523 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/functions.html:2384:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><div class=\"sqsrte-scaled-text-container\"><span class=\"sqsrte-scaled-text\"><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-large\">A Rich &amp; Rare way to celebrate</p></span></div></div>\nsource/functions.html:2401:  #block-022b4fe16584a2d68988 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/functions.html:2444:          #block-022b4fe16584a2d68988 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/functions.html:2877:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><h3 style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Private dining</h3><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><em>10 pax seated or 16 pax Canapé.<br><br></em>Here’s where deals are done, memories made and relationships forged. Timber, leather, fine china and tinkling glasses complement a menu of modern classics in a room as welcoming as it is intimate. </p></div>\nsource/functions.html:2894:  #block-4ed4fe8869be84a953c5 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/functions.html:2937:          #block-4ed4fe8869be84a953c5 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/functions.html:3362:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><h2 style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Full venue</h2><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><em>130 pax seated or 155 pax Canapé.<br><br></em>Celebrate elegantly with West End energy. An impressive entryway showcasing dry-aged beef and exceptional wine sets the scene for an unforgettable experience. Talk to our team about a bespoke menu bringing together the best of paddock, sea and vineyard to create an event your guests won’t want to end. </p></div>\nsource/functions.html:3379:  #block-007f67eb1c35f052117a .sqs-html-content {\nsource/functions.html:3422:          #block-007f67eb1c35f052117a .sqs-html-content {\nsource/functions.html:3764:      <p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">our Spaces</p>\nsource/functions.html:4228:        <h2\nsource/functions.html:4243:          <p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">65-70 pax seated or 80 pax canapé.</p>\nsource/functions.html:4296:        <h2\nsource/functions.html:4311:          <p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">60 pax seated or 75 pax canapé.</p>\nsource/functions.html:4364:        <h2\nsource/functions.html:4379:          <p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">15-20 pax seated or 35 pax canapé.</p>\nsource/functions.html:4432:        <h2\nsource/functions.html:4447:          <p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">10 pax seated or 16 pax canapé.</p>\nsource/functions.html:4801:    <h2 id=\"functions-enquiry\">Functions Enquiry</h2>\nsource/functions.html:4806:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Please complete the enquiry form and our functions manager will respond within one business day.</p></div>\nsource/functions.html:4823:  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1713246143314_3142 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/functions.html:4866:          #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1713246143314_3142 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/functions.html:4902:    {\"secureUrl\":\"https://guppy-turkey-esm7.squarespace.com\",\"collectionId\":\"64e6e86022513e4b25dca1a3\",\"formFieldFormats\":{\"initialNameOrder\":\"GIVEN_FIRST\",\"initialAddressFormat\":{\"id\":0,\"type\":\"ADDRESS\",\"country\":\"AU\",\"labelLocale\":\"en\",\"fields\":[{\"type\":\"FIELD\",\"label\":\"Address Line 1\",\"identifier\":\"Line1\",\"length\":0,\"required\":true,\"metadata\":{\"autocomplete\":\"address-line1\"}},{\"type\":\"SEPARATOR\",\"label\":\"\\n\",\"identifier\":\"Newline\",\"length\":0,\"required\":false,\"metadata\":{}},{\"type\":\"FIELD\",\"label\":\"Address Line 2\",\"identifier\":\"Line2\",\"length\