p;\">LUNCH &amp; DINNER</h1></div>\nsource/menu.html:2057:  #block-5798839f19368950d44b .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:2100:          #block-5798839f19368950d44b .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:2124:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\">From the bountiful oceans and farms of Queensland to the acclaimed cattle paddocks of Japan, our Chefs have rounded up the finest produce to create this exceptional menu. For the perfect accompaniments, please don’t hesitate to ask your waiter for recommendations of wines, whiskeys, and cocktails.</p></div>\nsource/menu.html:2141:  #block-d2ebdfe05415c618c522 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:2184:          #block-d2ebdfe05415c618c522 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:3197:</style><div class=\"fluid-engine fe-69b100f33b0f40403323b0ed\"><div class=\"fe-block fe-block-4106b96248a1f3ec5d9a\"><div class=\"sqs-block menu-block sqs-block-menu\" data-block-type=\"18\" id=\"block-4106b96248a1f3ec5d9a\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\nsource/menu.html:3199:<div class=\"menu-wrapper menu-style-classic\">\nsource/menu.html:3205:  <div class=\"menus \">\nsource/menu.html:3209:    class=\"menu js-menu menu-1-fe65402f-b85b-4b0b-8604-293d44adde48\"\nsource/menu.html:3215:      <div class=\"menu-section\">\nsource/menu.html:3219:        <div class=\"menu-items\">\nsource/menu.html:3221:            <div class=\"menu-item\">\nsource/menu.html:3223:                <span class=\"menu-item-price-top\">\nsource/menu.html:3230:              <div class=\"menu-item-title\">Artisan Sourdough Ciabatta (DFO, GFO)</div>\nsource/menu.html:3231:              <div class=\"menu-item-description\">Bone marrow butter</div>\nsource/menu.html:3234:                <div class=\"menu-item-price-bottom\">\nsource/menu.html:3245:            <div class=\"menu-item\">\nsource/menu.html:3247:                <span class=\"menu-item-price-top\">\nsource/menu.html:3254: