-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Westholme Wagyu Tartare MB4-5 Petit Tender<br></strong><em>Yolk, fresh horseradish, homemade potato crisps</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Scotch Fillet<br></strong><em>150+ days grain fed, Riverina, full blood Black Angus, <br> Glen Innes, New England Tablelands, NSW</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Tajima Wagyu Striploin MB6-7<br></strong><em>300+ day grain fed Wagyu from Tajima bloodline cattle of Hyogo Prefecture in Japan, crossbred with Angus/Holstein, F1-F4, and raised in Australia, Riverina Region, NSW</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Striploin A5 Japanese Wagyu MB12+<br></strong><em>650+ days grain fed, 100% full blood A5 Japanese Black Wagyu, Kagoshima Japan</em></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>R&amp;R Red Wine Jus</strong></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Bone Marrow Mash&nbsp;</strong></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Green Beans&nbsp;</strong></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Shoestring Fries&nbsp;</strong></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>Mixed Leaf Salad</strong></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"text-align: center; ; white-space:pre-wrap;\" data-rte-preserve-empty=\"true\"><strong>R&amp;R Cheesecake</strong></p></div>\nsource/menu.html:7447:  #block-d9f68ccb0ca436127e91 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:7490:          #block-d9f68ccb0ca436127e91 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:7537:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-small\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-highlight\" data-text-attribute-id=\"0df74c89-af29-4e22-8841-53056b0eda66\"><strong>ADD ONS</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-small\">Fried Egg <strong>5 </strong>Foie Gras <strong>40</strong> King Prawn <strong>12 </strong>Whole Live Lobster <strong>240 </strong>Blue Cheese <strong>10</strong></p></div>\nsource/menu.html:7554:  #block-593a8f85d83de1863b44 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:7597:          #block-593a8f85d83de1863b44 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:7818:</style><div class=\"fluid-engine fe-69b100f33b0f40403323b0f3\"><div class=\"fe-block fe-block-3a9f0ee9f1f43ab3d66a\"><div class=\"sqs-block menu-block sqs-block-menu\" data-block-type=\"18\" id=\"block-3a9f0ee9f1f43ab3d66a\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\">\nsource/menu.html:7820:<div class=\"menu-wrapper menu-style-classic\">\nsource/menu.html:7826:  <div class=\"menus \">\nsource/menu.html:7830:    class=\"menu js-menu menu-1-6267454e-3cd0-48f1-963e-62597c2fe639\"\nsource/menu.html:7836:      <div class=\"menu-section\">\nsource/menu.html:7839:        <div class=\"menu-section-header\">\nsource/menu.html:7840:          <div class=\"menu-section-title\">DESSERTS</div>\nsource/menu.html:7845:        <div class=\"menu-items\">\nsource/menu.html:7847:            <div class=\"menu-item\">\nsource/menu.html:7849:                <span class=\"menu-item-price-top\">\nsource/menu.html:7856:              <div class=\"menu-item-title\">Chocolate</div>\nsource/menu.html:7857:              <div class=\"menu-item-description\">Cocoa crumble, macadamia ice cream, meringue crackers, black flake salt</div>\nsource/menu.html:7860:                <div class=\"menu-item-price-bottom\">\nsource/menu.html:7871:            <div class=\"menu-item\">\nsource/menu.html:7873:                <span class=\"menu-item-price-top\">\nsource/menu.html:7880:              <div class=\"menu-item-title\">Vanilla Crème Brulée</div>\nsource/menu.html:7881:              <div class=\"menu-item-description\">Berries, biscotti</div>\nsource/menu.html:7884:                <div class=\"menu-item-price-bottom\">\nsource/menu.html:7895:            <div class=\"menu-item\">\nsource/menu.html:7897:                <span class=\"menu-item-price-top\">\nsource/menu.html:7904:              <div class=\"menu-item-title\">Coconut Panna Cotta</div>\nsource/menu.html:7905:              <div class=\"menu-item-description\">Dried edible flowers, strawberry, silky mango sauce</div>\nsource/menu.html:7908:                <div class=\"menu-item-price-bottom\">\nsource/menu.html:7919:            <div class=\"menu-item\">\nsource/menu.html:7921:                <span class=\"menu-item-price-top\">\nsource/menu.html:7928:              <div class=\"menu-item-title\">R&R Cheesecake</div>\nsource/menu.html:7929:              <div class=\"menu-item-description\">Salted caramel sauce</div>\nsource/menu.html:7932:                <div class=\"menu-item-price-bottom\">\nsource/menu.html:7943:            <div class=\"menu-item\">\nsource/menu.html:7945:                <span class=\"menu-item-price-top\">\nsource/menu.html:7952:              <div class=\"menu-item-title\">Pistachio</div>\nsource/menu.html:7953:              <div class=\"menu-item-description\">Pudding, syrup & praline, macadamia ice cream</div>\nsource/menu.html:7956:                <div class=\"menu-item-price-bottom\">\nsource/menu.html:7967:            <div class=\"menu-item\">\nsource/menu.html:7969:                <span class=\"menu-item-price-top\">\nsource/menu.html:7984:              <div class=\"menu-item-title\">One, two or three Cheeses</div>\nsource/menu.html:7985:              <div class=\"menu-item-description\">Our cheese is served with lavosh, muscatels, quince. Ask your waiter for todays cheese selection</div>\nsource/menu.html:7988:                <div class=\"menu-item-price-bottom\">\nsource/menu.html:8018:</div> <!-- END .menu-wrapper -->\nsource/menu.html:8229:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-small\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--darkAccent\"><em>Kids menu available upon request.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-small\"><em>10% Weekend surcharge (20% on public holidays). Card payment surcharge applies.</em></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"sqsrte-small\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--darkAccent\"><em>Please advise wait staff of any dietary requirements or allergies. Needs are catered for to the best of our ability, but the decision to consume a meal is the responsibility of the diner. Nuts, seafood, shellfish, sesame seeds, wheat, flour, eggs, fungi &amp; dairy products are all handled on these premises.</em></span></p></div>\nsource/menu.html:8246:  #block-4630839cb5327d364238 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:8289:          #block-4630839cb5327d364238 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:8938:            href=\"https://www.instagram.com/richandrare_brisbane/\"\nsource/menu.html:8940:            class=\"sqs-svg-icon--wrapper instagram-unauth\"\nsource/menu.html:8945:                <use class=\"sqs-use--icon\" xlink:href=\"/universal/svg/social-accounts.svg#instagram-unauth-icon\"></use>\nsource/menu.html:8946:                <use class=\"sqs-use--mask\" xlink:href=\"/universal/svg/social-accounts.svg#instagram-unauth-mask\"></use>\nsource/menu.html:8954:            href=\"http://facebook.com/richandrare.bne\"\nsource/menu.html:8956:            class=\"sqs-svg-icon--wrapper facebook-unauth\"\nsource/menu.html:8961:                <use class=\"sqs-use--icon\" xlink:href=\"/universal/svg/social-accounts.svg#facebook-unauth-icon\"></use>\nsource/menu.html:8962:                <use class=\"sqs-use--mask\" xlink:href=\"/universal/svg/social-accounts.svg#facebook-unauth-mask\"></use>\nsource/menu.html:8973:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><strong>OPEN 7 DAYS</strong><br>All Day Dining: 11:00am-late</p></div>\nsource/menu.html:8990:  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1722823170214_2896 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:9033:          #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1722823170214_2896 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:9057:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">10% Weekend surcharge (20% on Public Holidays). Card payment surcharge applies.</p></div>\nsource/menu.html:9074:  #block-c41f2ae0d7d3d617dc63 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:9117:          #block-c41f2ae0d7d3d617dc63 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:9141:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">FIND US<br>West Village Garden Pavilion<br>97 Boundary Street,<br>West End, Q 4101</p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">CAREERS<br><a href=\"/careers\">Employment</a></p><p class=\"sqsrte-small\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><br>BUSINESS OPPORTUNITIES<br><a href=\"https://www.tassisgroup.com.au/business-opportunities\" target=\"_blank\">Business Opportunities</a></p></div>\nsource/menu.html:9158:  #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1683680118894_8960 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:9201:          #block-yui_3_17_2_1_1683680118894_8960 .sqs-html-content {\nsource/menu.html:9275:      <h2 class=\"newsletter-form-header-title\">Subscribe</h2>\nsource/menu.html:9276:      <div class=\"newsletter-form-header-description\"><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Sign up to receive news and updates.</p></div>\nsource/menu.html:9314:    <d