id: 71
event: agent
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"The captures show a mostly black/white Squarespace system, Montserrat as the live font, square buttons, full-width image-led sections, white logo on dark hero, and official facts around West Village Garden Pavilion, 97 Boundary Street, all-day dining, SevenRooms bookings, Instagram/Facebook, menus/functions/contact. I’m going to preserve that but make the concept feel more refined through darker dining-room tones, restrained ivory surfaces, and a single warm metal accent."}

